# Whitelist-based exclusion: start by excluding everything, then re-include what is needed.
**

# Root files
!LICENSE.txt
!package.json
!readme.md
!changelog.md
!bunfig.toml

# Extension assets
!assets/**

# CLI binary
!bin/kilo.exe
!bin/kilo
!bin/.cli-version

# Compiled extension + webview
!dist/**

# Hermes + other docs shipped with extension
!docs/**
